data.title: Tyson Chandler, Basketball Player
data.meta_description: Tyson Chandler stats and bio. Stats averages season by season. Quick access to game by game stats.
data.text:
Tyson Chandler - Points

Tyson Chandler scores a career high 28 points (2012)

On November 26, 2012, Tyson Chandler set his career high in points in a NBA game. That day he scored 28 points in New York's road loss against Brooklyn, 96-89. He also had 10 rebounds, 1 assist, 2 steals. He shot 12/13 from two, shooting at 92.3% from the field. He also shot 4/4 from the free-throw line.

Tyson Chandler - Rebounds

Tyson Chandler grabs a career high 28 rebounds (2013)

On February 27, 2013, Tyson Chandler set his career high in rebounds in a NBA game. That day he grabbed 28 rebounds in New York's home win against Golden State, 109-105. He also had 16 points, 1 assist, 2 steals and 1 block.

Tyson Chandler - Assists

Tyson Chandler gives a career high 6 assists (2002)

On April 11, 2002, Tyson Chandler set his career high in assists in a NBA game. That day he dished 6 assists in Chicago's road win against New York, 101-104. He also had 16 points, 15 rebounds, 1 steal and 3 blocks.

Tyson Chandler - Steals

Tyson Chandler has a career high 5 steals (2003)

On March 18, 2003, Tyson Chandler set his career high in steals in a NBA game. That day he reached 5 steals in Chicago's home win against Atlanta, 103-78. He also had 13 points, 11 rebounds.

Tyson Chandler - Blocks

Tyson Chandler blocks a career high 7 shots (2003)

On February 12, 2003, Tyson Chandler tied his career high in blocks in a NBA game. That day he went for 7 blocks in Chicago's road loss against Philadelphia, 119-111. He also had 21 points, 17 rebounds.

Tyson Chandler - Efficiency

Tyson Chandler records a career high 43 efficiency rating (2013)

On February 27, 2013, Tyson Chandler set his career high in efficiency in a NBA game. That day he accomplished 43 efficiency in New York's home win against Golden State, 109-105. He also had 16 points, 28 rebounds and 1 assist.
